name: Princess Iron Fan
skill: Deals 1602/1962 DMG to the row of enemy directly in front, with a moderate chance of inflicting Burn.

additional_data.description: A spirit who owns the treasured iron fan from "Journey to the West." When Sun Wukong came to borrow it, she did everything in her power to stop him. After many bouts of deception and trickery between the two, she finally gave up when her husband was defeated and forfeited the fan to the monkey king. Since then she's been training herself to live a more noble life.

main: "It doesn't matter how low I have to go—I will have my revenge."
skill: "With these two, I can stir up quite the gust!"
limit_break: "I can feel my heart becoming more pure."
